document_data.Relationships:
He was a loyal member of the [[Lords' Alliance]], and had close ties to both [[Neverwinter]] and [[Waterdeep]]. He was a friend of [[Gundren Rockseeker]].{{Cite adventurers league/In Volo's Wake|38}}

He was a member of the knightly [[Hallwinter]] family{{Cite web/D&D Beyond/Vecna: Nest of the Eldritch Eye}} and had an adopted daughter named [[Alana Hallwinter|Alana]].{{Cite adventurers league/In Volo's Wake|15}}

As a member of the town council of Phandalin, he was well respected and trusted by the townsfolk. He seemed to get along well with fellow councilors [[Trilena Stonehill]] and [[Halia Thornton]], but not so much with councilor [[Harbin Wester]], whom he saw as fundamentally corrupt.
